profile:
Kitchen Magician was born as a result of a dear 'little old lady' who was ashamed of her kitchen cabinets but could not afford to replace or reface them. She was too embarrassed to invite friends over anymore.Seeing a wonderful opportunity to utilize his wide array of skills, and motivated by a desire to be of service to others, Doug Harrison, the company founder, wrote his guiding motto that evening:

"To give you an attractive kitchen... as inexpensively as possible."
